It features a spherical logo with the words "OFF" in bold, a contrasting border, and a raised weave. Additionally, it features a rubber backing, which protects it from developing curls.

The Pin for Love concept celebrates connection and little moments of affection, and here it arrives as mini Labubu pendants with designs coded from A to M. Each box keeps the surprise intact while the character’s toothy grin and tall ears deliver that mischievous look fans know by heart.

The sealed case includes fourteen blind boxes from the A to M assortment, and there is a secret chase that nods to the theme of love for collectors who enjoy the hunt. At roughly hand sized with detailed stitching and painted features, these minis carry a lot of personality in a small format without losing Labubu’s storybook edge.

title: Balenciaga Triple S Silver Red (2018)
description:
Experience the epitome of luxury streetwear with the Balenciaga Triple S Silver Red, released on February 3, 2018. This sneaker captures the essence of Balenciaga's innovative design philosophy, featuring a striking combination of silver and red that sets it apart from the crowd. The Triple S Silver Red is a bold exploration of color and form, embodying the brand's commitment to pushing the boundaries of sneaker culture.

This iteration of the Triple S sneaker is renowned for its layered, chunky sole and a blend of materials that create a rich, textured look. The silver and red colorway adds a dynamic element to the design, making it a vibrant choice for those looking to make a statement. It's a reflection of Balenciaga's flair for combining unconventional aesthetics with high-quality craftsmanship, offering a sneaker that's as daring as it is desirable.

title: Neiti - Duo Wheat
description: The Neiti model reinterprets an iconic leather goods braiding technique by softening it with wave-like undulating lines, along with interconnecting smooth and grained tone-on-tone leathers. Clever folds give the mini-bag its shape and volume.

description: With its rounded shape, foam padding, and hand-stitching, the “Numéro Dix” is a nod to the equestrian codes of saddlery. The canvas edition is cut from flecked wool that combines two shades of thread and leather trim accents.

title: Cyme - Beige Canvas
description: This sculptured tote bag featuring waves, folds, and curves can be used in two ways. Basket-style, with its sides open and straps on the outside, or As a flower-like closed bag, with its sides tucked in and its straps crossed on the inside.

title: Béri - Onda Fresh Almond
description: Obtained by folding four pieces of leather and forming the handle, the “Béri” model exudes a strong yet sophisticated style with its tailored base and central clasp.
